00:18:31,890 --> 00:18:32,490
<font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>什麼?</b></font>

301
00:18:32,850 --> 00:18:34,510
<font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我一時腦熱…</b></font>

302
00:18:35,050 --> 00:18:38,350
